## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives on globalization. The information is subject to the biases of the sources used, and the rapidly changing nature of global economic dynamics may affect the relevance of some findings. Additionally, the report does not delve into specific case studies or regional analyses, which could provide more detailed insights into the effects of globalization.